4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to prepare them for a career as a data scientist. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also includes practice solving real-life cases and mastering industry-standard tools. The duration of the course is 16 weeks, with classes held three times a week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion, students will receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. There are no prerequisites for this course, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop